 />\nI) 指 明 期 間 內 停 止售 賣 供 在 處 所內 進食 或 飲 用 的 食物 及飲<br />\r品<br />\r\na. 在任何時間，<strong>停止售賣或供應</strong>供在餐飲業務的處所內進食或飲用<br />\r的食物或飲品<br />\r\nb. 在任何時間，<strong>關閉</strong>售賣或供應食物或飲品，<strong>供在該處所內</strong>進食或<br />\r飲用的處所或該處所的<strong>部分範圍</strong><br />\n<br />\nI)a. 係話停賣 &ldquo;上碟&rdquo; 形式，姐係淨係賣外賣包裝。<br />\nI)b. 係話封坐位，但就指明係為左唔比食同一間餐廳賣嘅野食嘅坐位。但同時imply 封埋同一個比人自攜食物嘅坐位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"即係本身無賣開野食或野飲嘅地方就可以放開比其他人入內進食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係咁囉"},{"pid":"8e615cccc654a5382e5e3293adc415cb222ff66a","tid":2131421,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又岩wo"},{"pid":"bb46ae2be57cc6f22b832d5c1b6b8c3c96ed6b9e","tid":2131421,"uid":91918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e0dc22212a04917c6dcddec9667813dadd8925","tid":2131421,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"同一間餐廳賣野比你食，又提供座位就係堂食<br />\n咁如果唔係同一間餐廳呢？去美心食黃店嘅食物呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"唔好以為自己好有見解，你真係ＯＮ９架！"},{"pid":"f939ad6a9c6a2562883f19f04bd610125ba9201a","tid":2131421,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff037631e38ab8e4c51575c2ec1c030c4cf4de9d","tid":2131421,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:11:49.000Z","msg":"拎 A 餐廳既外賣去 B 餐廳食又好似唔犯法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"但另一間餐廳都唔開堂食<br />\n邊度會有位坐<br />\n再講你自己拎野入黎食<br />\n有冇疫情呢件事 間餐廳都唔比你咁做啦<br />\n唔通開善堂"},{"pid":"0ff5b2018084414ac3b1bff6d0d40fe5e96be084","tid":2131421,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"唔好怪樓主啦 其實佢仲係小學生黎<br />\n我係佢表哥 唔係好親個隻<br />\n佢有少少低智個d唔好講啦<br />\n佢讀特殊學校個d都無謂提<br />\n不過大家放過佢啦 佢仲係讀緊小三<br />\n佢老豆老母都好辛苦 要照顧樓主<br />\n佢細細個已經食雞唔食雞皮 食橙食埋橙皮<br />\n我代佢係呢度向大家道歉一聲"},{"pid":"7ee97b4501c8e55c0ca59699b764f176754cab52","tid":2131421,"uid":364376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba4a5d6c832127fcedc697aecd99652a5644b6ce","tid":2131421,"uid":50504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T01:12:55.000Z","msg":"樓主咁都諗到，壞過凱婷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"一次過食2個飯盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}